    "asOf": "2023-05-18",
    "date": "2023-06-12T18:15:18Z",
    "text": "Bicycle Commuter Act of 2023 \n\nThis bill reinstates and expands the tax exclusion for employer-provided fringe benefits for bicycle commuting. It allows employees a bicycle commuting benefit equal to 30% of parking fringe benefits.\n\nThe bill repeals the suspension period (2018-2025) applicable to such tax exclusion and revises definitions applicable to bicycle commuting benefits to make electric bicycles and certain scooters eligible for the tax exclusion."
